      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PATH TO GREATNESS (3) is a well performed pacer who galloped from the standing start but still managed to win last time at this circuit and distance. Better suited back to a mobile start and goes well third-up so should be further improved. Take beating from a good draw. APPLIED NZ (9) made it four placings on the trot at this venue when coming from a wide barrier for second last week, finishing just 1.2 metres from the winner. Draws on the back line this time but the recent consistency is hard to knock. FIRE RAISER (1) will be fitter for recent racing and gets the ace draw so has to come into calculations. SMARTER THAN YOU (2) is another better served by tonight's draw having come from this barrier to place here last month.",
